    "body": "I just released a temporal hotfix. Please upgrade `@nomiclabs/buidler-ethers` to `2.0.2` to be able to use Buidler while we implement a proper fix.\r\n\r\nThe only negative impact of the hotfix is that transactions can't use the entire block gas limit for now. If you are being affected by this, you can work around it by adding the `blockGasLimit` and `gas` fields to the `buidlerevm` network, making sure that `blockGasLimit` is at least 1M higher than `gas`.",
